<view class="page-shell section-page">
  <view class="section-card glass-card">
    <view class="section-title">请选择当前标段</view>
    <view class="section-subtitle">进入上报前先确认所属标段，隐患信息会按标段进入对应后台管理。</view>

    <view class="section-grid">
      <view
        wx:for="{{sections}}"
        wx:key="code"
        class="section-item {{item.activeClass}}"
        data-code="{{item.code}}"
        bindtap="handleSectionTap"
      >
        <view class="section-code">{{item.code}}</view>
        <view class="section-name">{{item.name}}</view>
        <view class="section-state">{{item.stateText}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-note">选择完成后将直接进入隐患上报页面，后续仍可切换标段。</view>
  </view>
</view>
